OL,3,CBaby died sleeping with mum's
OL,4,Cboyfriend after drugs binge
OL,6,FA seven-week-old baby girl died while
OL,7,Fco-sleeping with her mother's
OL,8,Fboyfriend after he had taken a
OL,9,Fcocktail of drugs, a Coroner's Court
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FBaby Heather Katie Mathers was on the
OL,13,Fchild protection register amid
OL,14,Fconcerns for her well-being when she
OL,15,Fwas found dead at 7am on 26 August,
OL,16,F2019 at a house in Lurgan.
