OL,3,CBaby died sleeping with mum's
OL,4,Cboyfriend after drugs binge
OL,6,FOn the morning she was found dead
OL,7,FHeather Katie was sharing a bed with
OL,8,Fher mother's boyfriend. Her mother `
OL,9,FRebecca Mathers ` was sleeping on a
OL,10,Fsofa in another room.
OL,12,FMs Mathers had previously been warned
OL,13,Fby Social Services not to have any
OL,14,Fcontact with her then boyfriend `
OL,15,FCurtis Whitla.
OL,17,FAn inquest into the baby's death heard
OL,18,Fthat Mr Whitla had taken cocaine,
OL,19,Fcannabis and prescription drugs at
OL,20,Fsome stage before falling asleep with
OL,21,FHeather Katie.
