OL,6,FThe baby had been on the at risk
OL,7,Fregister for potential neglect since
OL,8,Fbirth.
OL,10,FFollowing a case conference with
OL,11,FSocial Services just before her birth
OL,12,Fit was agreed that Heather Katie could
OL,13,Fstay in her mother's care, subject to
OL,14,Fa number of restrictions.
OL,16,FOne of those restrictions was not to
OL,17,Fassociate with Mr Whitla.
