OL,3,CBaby died sleeping with mum's
OL,4,Cboyfriend after drugs binge
OL,6,FBut Social Services became aware the
OL,7,Fpair were still in contact and became
OL,8,Fincreasingly concerned about the
OL,9,Fbaby's wellbeing.
OL,11,FOn July 30, when Heather Katie was
OL,12,Fthree weeks old, Social Services
OL,13,Fdecided to file papers for an Interim
OL,14,FCare Order, which would give them
OL,15,Fparental responsibility.
OL,17,FBut at the time of the child's death,
OL,18,Falmost four weeks later, the papers
OL,19,Fhad not been filed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
