OL,6,FAlso, no social worker had been
OL,7,Fassigned to the case after the
OL,8,Fprevious social worker went on planned
OL,9,Fmedical leave at the start of August.
OL,11,FCoroner Ann-Louise Toal said that it
OL,12,Fwould have seemed appropriate that
OL,13,F"arrangements would be put in place to
OL,14,Fhave the case transferred to another
OL,15,Fassigned worker at the commencement of
OL,16,F(the previous social workers) leave."
