OL,6,FShe added that it also would have been
OL,7,Fappropriate, given the increasing
OL,8,Fconcerns, for steps to have been taken
OL,9,Fto expedite the completion of the
OL,10,FInterim Care Order report.
OL,12,FCoroner Toal ruled that this was a
OL,13,Fsudden unexpected death, caused, on
OL,14,Fthe balance of probabilities, by co-
OL,15,Fsleeping.
OL,17,FShe issued a warning about the dangers
OL,18,Fof co-sleeping with children under the
OL,19,Fage of 12 months.
